com.sitewhere.rest.model.device.event.request

Class DeviceStateChangeCreateRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sitewhere.rest.model.device.event.request.DeviceEventCreateRequest
      • com.sitewhere.rest.model.device.event.request.DeviceStateChangeCreateRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDeviceEventCreateRequest, IDeviceStateChangeCreateRequest, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DeviceRegistrationRequest

    public class DeviceStateChangeCreateRequest
extends DeviceEventCreateRequest
implements IDeviceStateChangeCreateRequest, java.io.Serializable
    Represents a change in state for a device. This may be a statement of the current state (i.e. a piece of hardware is unavailable) or a request for change of system state (i.e the device requests registration in the system).
